claim.claim-text:
An electronic apparatus, comprising:
a flexible circuit(s);
a component(s) mounted on the flexible circuit(s); and
a casing having an opening(s) for accommodating the component(s);
wherein the flexible circuit(s) is exposed from the opening in a state where the component is not provided in position.

The electronic apparatus according to claim 1 or 2, wherein

a plurality of the flexible circuits are provided;

the flexible circuits not being superposed together within the opening.

The electronic apparatus according to claim 8, wherein

the nameplate is mounted on the flexible circuit(s);

the battery being mounted on the nameplate.
